cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you reference this project, please cite it as below."
title: "Box Dweller (盒中人): an LLM-editable 3D world"
abstract: >-
  A 3D world designed around how a language model operates rather than around a
  human player: a two-tier primitive protocol with runtime macro registration,
  structured JSON as the sole interface, and fixed-length world snapshots.
